des: Everyone knows about Santa's Naughty and Nice Lists but did you know there's a secret 3rd List? There is: The Snotty List. This quiz is designed to weed out the Snotty from the Nice. Take it now and see which list you belong on! And visit www.TheSnottyList.com to find out more!
